Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------NEXT-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.24,0:00:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你是那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  难道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日叶的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚斯荷丽特的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚斯荷丽特也长这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你有太多的话想说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对还是个孩子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着  以为你消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年后却突然出现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把说是我的孩子的明日叶留下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又再次消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得太不负责了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为可以再次见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天试着做了锡兰肉桂卷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露蒂  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是锡兰肉桂卷哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日叶的妈妈  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  明日叶戴着的那个发饰是妖魔界的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难办了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难办指的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨晚所遇到的人  明日叶的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们尤格瓦尔兰王国国王梅尔契丽妲一世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亚斯塔露蒂殿下的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  也…也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉大人  冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下和明日叶  是同母异父的姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下和明日叶居然是姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下的私生子么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是正室的孩子  当成养子就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要藏到在人间界的直哉大人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事请对公主殿下保密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早饭已经吃过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  露蒂完全没有吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是因为妈妈没有来派对而失落着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日叶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  关于昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的事知道了些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没怎么和妈妈说过话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有很多很多想说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也是  重要的话没有对那个人说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着一定要说出口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于明日叶的妈妈  有必须要跟你好好说明的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才再次见到的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你有太多的话想说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有错的应该是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没能见到露蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的完全不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.07,0:06:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也不至于这么生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再遇到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想再见见他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  伊索尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想确定一下今晚侍寝的人选
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您意下如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失  失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饮料拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  新来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我叫直美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是妈妈的后宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日叶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一位是可爱的淑女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我妹妹明日叶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为像姐姐一样的美人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去见国王陛下  是么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然情况是现在这样  但一般来说谒见还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也想再见到那个人一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着明日叶  想三人一起好好说说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要潜入的话  就从后宫的桃色蔷薇馆里进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔妲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连艾尔芙也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后宫的警备相对王宫来说比较薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变装之后混进那里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变  变装？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上这个混进去的话就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（这不是女仆装么）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔妲  艾尔芙  过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不穿的话怎么知道合不合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  大家都以为爸爸是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没想到会是被要求以这个样子潜入城堡里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样子一来也不会被怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快开始来找梅尔契在哪里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高170cm左右的黑发美男子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然20来岁了但看上去只有10多岁的童颜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合女装的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵越短越好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚指定的又是这么详细呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  完全就像是特定某人的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  后宫里有这样的男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他找出来  就是侍寝选定官的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里看上去也不像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下一个  明日叶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  这个…也就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  突然之间干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请老实一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是男的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  假发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚为陛下侍寝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为陛下侍寝么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我弟弟  可以和我一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侍寝的人带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我要求的是一样的男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连亚斯荷丽特也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  特地跑到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想继续抱怨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下  不  梅尔契丽妲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事没对你说  所以才来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想对你说这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子  是我救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给了我活下去的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生下了这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这孩子交给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我和爸爸这么幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔契
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要叫我亲爱的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前第一次见到梅尔契时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这么和我说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于你姐姐们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家为了争夺王位最后都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说早知道会那样的话  没出生在王族就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把明日叶带到我身边来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让她卷入王族的纷争里去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让她和身为妹妹的公主殿下相互仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子很讨厌我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下才没有讨厌你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:14:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  直哉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  这么晚才回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这样子进展很顺利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  多亏了大家的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早才回来  你把自己当谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下看来很生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日叶  要去上学了  快点去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个周末不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个周末过得舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去心情非常不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她对上星期派对的事还…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定她非常期待国王陛下的驾临呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  露…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔契丽妲国王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天将要进行特别教学参观
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  请安静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我会仔细地来为大家讲解一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  恩雅校长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们当中有些人的家长由于公务繁忙无法来参加周末的派对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可能让她们觉得有些寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们紧急决定在今天进行正式的教学参观
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎么繁忙  父母肯定是想见到自己孩子的成长的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我能现在联络一下母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一整天无论何时都是教学参观哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都和露蒂一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都穿着华丽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有干劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露蒂的妈妈穿的最朴素呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是穿的太朴素了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教学参观时穿什么衣服合适真让人头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了陛下  大家都很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  露蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托殿下的妈妈的福  我的妈妈也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要谢谢公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我什么都没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要谢的话  也要谢国王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有没有做好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲  这些行李是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道教学参观该穿什么来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就把能带的东西都带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露蒂  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是露蒂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想找个时间给你于是一直带在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一直没有时机给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个请由母亲保管着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我去母亲那里留宿的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能抱着它一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次你能亲自给我的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈我绝对会来看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是于是于是  露蒂妈妈的西装很合身看上去非常帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  露蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲无论穿什么都是非常有型的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教学参观真的很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是最好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你亲了妈妈的额头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和好后一定得亲一下额头的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要教公主殿下这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔原流和好的额头一吻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是说不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我说清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛  又不会少块肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:58.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\bord4}待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.64,0:23:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真闲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着很闲  醒着也很闲
